it is debatable=\r\n whether it is bad or good. My guess is that the 0.0001% to whom such a thi=\r\nng happens will figure out how to deal with it.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&=\r\nnbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *=\r\n&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;As I always say, I am not a missionary. How many people do ho=\r\nmam and what rules they follow, do not concern me. I am just an enabler. I =\r\nmerely\n make some resources available. People are free to take it or leave =\r\nit. Also, people are free to follow any rules set by their gurus or elders =\r\nor just their inner voice. They need not pay heed to my 2 cents.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;=\r\nbr&gt;In the end, every soul has its path to traverse.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Happy Vija=\r\nya Dasami friends!&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Best regards,&lt;br&gt;Narasimha&lt;br&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;A=\r\nstrology &amp; Spirituality Resources: http://www.VedicAstrologer.org &lt;br&gt;-=\r\n-------&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;--- In vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com, &quot;ashutosh.srikant=\r\nh&quot; &lt;ashutosh.srikanth@...&gt; wrote:&lt;br&gt;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&gt; My pranams to all.&lt;=\r\nbr&gt;&gt; I have been performing weekly havan for more than a year and half.&lt;=\r\nbr&gt;&gt; I want to point out certain things related to havan so that it can =\r\nbe done as per shastra by others too.&lt;br&gt;&gt; I am using a conversation tha=\r\nt in fact took place to bring out these relevant points.&lt;br&gt;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&gt; So=\r\nmetime back there was informal &quot;prashNa&quot; session whose summary I am\n presen=\r\nting below:&lt;br&gt;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&gt; [South Indians might be familiar with similar &quot;=\r\nashTamangala prashNa&quot; conducted in temples when something goes wrong - call=\r\ned as dosha.]&lt;br&gt;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&gt; PrashNa conductor: There seems to be a dosha.=\r\n.. Hmm... let me see... Hmm.. Yes... You seem to be performing some kind of=\r\n Agni karya at your home r